      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n(1 comment)\n\n>Why not just move the set default value from mdd_prepare() to mdd_init0()? I think the latter one is proper place to initialize default values.\n\nBecause default value is only one of the possible troubles. Generally it is better if options from PARAMS are applied after devices initialisation.",
